title: 9-Foot Ceilings, Vintage Moldings, Hardwood Floors
posting_body: ['308 Fourth Ave.', 'S, Seattle, WA 98104', 'Addison on Fourth is a low-income apartment community located in the heart of downtown Seattle between 4th Ave S. and Jackson street.', 'Addison is located close to the Seattle stadiums, major transit, restaurants, shopping and much more.', 'The International District and Pioneer Square are just blocks away.', "You'll enjoy on-site amenities such as the resident lounge, fitness facility, and on-site management means convenience for you.", 'Call or visit us online to schedule your tour of Addison and learn about our low-income community.', "With a location close to several art galleries, restaurants, cafes, and landmarks, you'll love calling Addison on Fourth your new home!", 'We are a low-income community and participate in the', 'Affordable Housing Program.', 'Income & Student restrictions apply.', 'Specific documentation may be required in order to verify eligibility for this program.', 'Income (Gross pretax) /Occupancy', 'Restrictions:', '1 Occupant: $54,360 annually', '2 Occupants: $62,160 annually', '3 Occupants: $69,900 annually', 'Student Restrictions:', 'All occupants cannot be a full-time student or have been in a full-time student for more than 5 months out of the last calendar year.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Renovated Interiors', 'Large Windows', 'Vintage Moldings', '9-Foot Ceilings', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Convection oven/Microwaves and Dishwashers', 'Community Features:', 'On-Site Management', 'Pet Friendly', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Media Room', 'Translation Service Available', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
